name: Deregistered land
text: §657-33.5  Deregistered land.  In no event shall the period of limitations provided in this part begin prior to the date and time of deregistration for deregistered land.  The terms "date and time of deregistration" and "deregistered land" as used in this section shall have the same meaning as in section 501-20. [L 2009, c 120, §4; am L 2012, c 121, §8]
